1319
01:21:20,523 --> 01:21:21,824
- Well, I don't--

1320
01:21:21,824 --> 01:21:22,990
- Because there's a very good prep school

1321
01:21:22,990 --> 01:21:25,200
right outside of town,
be a nice way to segue

1322
01:21:25,200 --> 01:21:26,880
to being a family, having him close enough

1323
01:21:26,880 --> 01:21:29,040
to visit on the weekends.

1324
01:21:29,040 --> 01:21:30,200
He'd probably get a much better education

1325
01:21:30,200 --> 01:21:31,243
than what he's getting know,

1326
01:21:31,243 --> 01:21:33,160
and there are also excellent
schools for girls here too.

1327
01:21:33,160 --> 01:21:35,490
My nieces attended St. Meredith's.

1328
01:21:35,490 --> 01:21:38,290
You can ask them about it
later at the rehearsal dinner.

1329
01:21:41,230 --> 01:21:42,063
- Excuse me.

1330
01:21:48,287 --> 01:21:49,120
- [Daughter] I do not.

1331
01:21:49,120 --> 01:21:50,330
- [Mother] Yes you do, two or three hours

1332
01:21:50,330 --> 01:21:51,650
